<section class="cta-section" id="download" aria-labelledby="cta-title">
  <h2 id="cta-title" class="cta-headline">Stop leaking your email on screen.</h2>
  <p class="cta-sub">Tested on Claude, ChatGPT, and Gmail. Works on any Chromium or Zen Browser-based site where email addresses appear in the DOM.</p>

  <button class="download-btn open-download-modal">
