    Download Extension
  </button>

  <p class="cta-footnote">
    Free &amp; open source &middot; Chromium &amp; Zen Browser &middot;
    <a href="https://github.com/pc-style/mailhush" target="_blank" rel="noopener">source code</a>
  </p>
</section>
